---
title: Fantastical Fig, Balsamic and Red Wine Chicken with Hasselback Potatoes and Scrummy Yummy Green Beans
description: Enjoy the wondrous flavours of this Chicken in a Fantastical Fig, Balsamic and Red Wine Sauce with Hasselback Potatoes and Scrummy Yummy Green Beans.
